translations._my_vocab.add_adjective.heading: Add adjective
translations._my_vocab.add_adjective.help_1: Enter the base, t- and long forms.
translations._my_vocab.add_adjective.help_2: The comparative and superlative may also be provided, or can be omitted (so "mest" and "mere" plus the base form are assumed).
translations._my_vocab.add_adjective.help_3: The inflection isn't saved; it's just something that can be a helpful shortcut to entering the forms. For example, use something like "-t, -e" for just the t- and long forms, or e.g. "-t, -e -mere, -mest" if you also want the comparative and superlative.

translations._my_vocab.shared.language.label: Language:
All three tenses must be filled in
If you enter "1" for Present, then the answers are filled in as per group 1; use "2" for group 2. The answers can be edited before they are submitted.

For example, if you think that the verb is regular group 1, then type "1", press enter, then press enter again. But if you think it's almost group 1, but not quite, then type "1", press enter, edit, and press enter again.

translations.welcome.para_1: Word Filth hjelper deg med å bli god på dansk, med periodisk repetisjon. Det er en innebygd liste med mer enn 300 verb, men du kan også legge til egne ord og uttrykk.
translations.welcome.para_2: Word Filth bruker "Logg på med Google" for å lagre resultatene dine online. Du kan alltid laste ned dine egne data.
